    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Entreprise commune «Hydrogène propre»"@fr, "Съвместно предприятие „Чист водород“"@bg, "An Comhghnóthas um Hidrigin Ghlan"@ga, "Wspólne Przedsięwzięcie na rzecz Czystego Wodoru"@pl, "L-Impriża Konġunta Idroġenu Nadif"@mt, "Det gemensamma företaget för förnybar vätgas"@sv, "Fællesforetagendet for ren brint"@da, "Gemeenschappelijke Onderneming “Schone waterstof”"@nl, "Spoločný podnik pre čistý vodík"@sk, "Tiszta Hidrogén Közös Vállalkozás"@hu, "Impresa comune «Idrogeno pulito»"@it, "Společný podnik pro čistý vodík"@cs, "Skupno podjetje za čisti vodik"@sl, "Zajedničko poduzeće za čisti vodik"@hr, "Întreprinderea comună pentru un hidrogen curat"@ro, "Švariojo vandenilio bendroji įmonė"@lt, "Gemeinsames Unternehmen für sauberen Wasserstoff"@de, "Empresa Común para un Hidrógeno Limpio"@es, "Κοινή επιχείρηση «Καθαρό υδρογόνο»"@el, "Empresa Comum do Hidrogénio Limpo"@pt, "Clean Hydrogen Joint Undertaking"@en, "Puhtaan vedyn yhteisyritys"@fi, "Saastevaba vesiniku ühisettevõte"@et, "Kopuzņēmums “Tīrs ūdeņradis”"@lv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Clean Hydrogen Joint Undertaking is a public-private partnership which contributes to the general objectives of the Horizon Europe Regulation. Its general objectives are: to contribute to the objectives set out in the 2030 Climate Target Plan and the European Green Deal, by raising the EU’s ambition on reducing greenhouse gas emissions to at least 55% below 1990 levels by 2030 and climate neutrality by 2050; to contribute to the implementation of the 2020 European Commission’s Hydrogen Strategy for a climate neutral Europe; to strengthen the competitiveness of the Union clean hydrogen value chain; to stimulate clean hydrogen production, distribution, storage and end use applications."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "10.2843"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "EG"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "9246"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "CHJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001647"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "CHJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "CHJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "CHJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "CH JU"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CHJU_2021_0>;
