    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Ευρωπαϊκή Αρχή Εργασίας"@el, "An tÚdarás Eorpach Saothair"@ga, "European Labour Authority"@en, "Autorité européenne du travail"@fr, "Evropský orgán pro pracovní záležitosti"@cs, "Europese Arbeidsautoriteit"@nl, "Evropski organ za delo"@sl, "Europeiska arbetsmyndigheten"@sv, "Europos darbo institucija"@lt, "Autorità europea del lavoro"@it, "Autoritatea Europeană a Muncii"@ro, "Europejski Urząd ds. Pracy"@pl, "Euroopa Tööjõuamet"@et, "L-Awtorità Ewropea tax-Xogħol"@mt, "Európai Munkaügyi Hatóság"@hu, "Europäische Arbeitsbehörde"@de, "Autoridade Europeia do Trabalho"@pt, "Autoridad Laboral Europea"@es, "Европейски орган по труда"@bg, "Eiropas Darba iestāde"@lv, "Euroopan työviranomainen"@fi, "Europsko nadzorno tijelo za rad"@hr, "Európsky orgán práce"@sk, "Den Europæiske Arbejdsmarkedsmyndighed"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Labour Authority ensures that EU rules on labour mobility and social security coordination are enforced in a fair and effective way and makes it easier for citizens and businesses to reap the benefits of the internal market."@en;
