    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Agência da União Europeia para o Programa Espacia"@pt, "Οργανισμός της Ευρωπαϊκής Ένωσης για το Διαστημικό Πρόγραμμα"@el, "Gníomhaireacht an Aontais Eorpaigh um an gClár Spáis"@ga, "Eiropas Savienības Kosmosa programmas aģentūra"@lv, "Agentura Evropské unie pro Kosmický program"@cs, "Agence de l’Union européenne pour le programme spatial"@fr, "Agentur der Europäischen Union für das Weltraumprogramm"@de, "Agenzia dell’Unione europea per il programma spaziale"@it, "Euroopan unionin avaruusohjelmavirasto"@fi, "Euroopa Liidu Kosmoseprogrammi Amet"@et, "Aġenzija tal-Unjoni Ewropea għall-Programm Spazjali"@mt, "Agencja Unii Europejskiej ds. Programu Kosmicznego"@pl, "Europeiska unionens rymdprogrambyrå"@sv, "Agencija Europske unije za svemirski program"@hr, "Agencija Evropske unije za vesoljski program"@sl, "Agentschap van de Europese Unie voor het ruimtevaartprogramma"@nl, "Az Európai Unió Űrprogramügynöksége"@hu, "Агенция на Европейския съюз за космическата програма"@bg, "Agentúra Európskej únie pre vesmírny program"@sk, "Den Europæiske Unions Agentur for Rumprogrammet"@da, "Agencia de la Unión Europea para el Programa Espacial"@es, "Agenția Uniunii Europene pentru Programul spațial"@ro, "Europos Sąjungos kosmoso programos agentūra"@lt, "European Union Agency for the Space Programme"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The core mission of the European Union Agency for the Space Programme (EUSPA) is to implement the EU Space Programme and to provide reliable, safe and secure space-related services, maximising their socio-economic benefits for European society and business. By fostering the development of innovative and competitive upstream and downstream sectors and engaging with the entire EU Space community, EUSPA is driving innovation-based growth in the European economy and contributing to the safety of EU citizens and the security of the Union and its Member States, while at the same time reinforcing the EU’s strategic autonomy."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "9206"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "10.2878"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "TS"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "EUSPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>, "COB0001637"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "EUSPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "EUSPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "GAL"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "GSA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>;
