    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Wspólne Przedsięwzięcie na rzecz Inicjatywy w dziedzinie Innowacji w Ochronie Zdrowia"@pl, "Κοινή επιχείρηση «Πρωτοβουλία για την Καινοτομία στην Υγεία»"@el, "Cъвместно предприятие „Инициатива за иновативно здравеопазване“"@bg, "Empresa Comum da Iniciativa Saúde Inovadora"@pt, "Innovatív Egészségügy Közös Vállalkozás"@hu, "Společný podnik iniciativy pro inovativní zdravotnictví"@cs, "Kopuzņēmums “Inovatīvas veselības aprūpes iniciatīva”"@lv, "Innovatiivse tervishoiu algatuse ühisettevõte"@et, "Empresa Común para la Iniciativa de Salud Innovadora"@es, "Novatoriškų sveikatos sprendimų iniciatyvos bendroji įmonė"@lt, "Innovative Health Initiative Joint Undertaking"@en, "L-Impriża Konġunta Inizjattiva għal Saħħa Innovattiva"@mt, "Comhghnóthas an Tionscnaimh um Shláinte Nuálach"@ga, "Entreprise commune «Initiative en matière de santé innovante»"@fr, "Întreprinderea comună „Inițiativa pentru inovare în domeniul sănătății”"@ro, "Gemeenschappelijke Onderneming “Initiatief voor innovatieve gezondheidszorg”"@nl, "Det gemensamma företaget för initiativet för innovativ hälsa"@sv, "Skupno podjetje za pobudo za inovativno zdravje"@sl, "Zajedničko poduzeće za inicijativu za inovativno zdravlje"@hr, "Impresa comune «Iniziativa per l’innovazione nel settore della salute»"@it, "Gemeinsames Unternehmen „Initiative zu Innovation im Gesundheitswesen“"@de, "Spoločný podnik pre iniciatívu Inovatívne zdravotníctvo"@sk, "Fællesforetagendet for initiativet om innovativ sundhed"@da, "Innovatiivisen terveydenhuollon aloitteen yhteisyritys"@fi;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Innovative Health Initiative Joint Undertaking is a public-private partnership which contributes to the general objectives of the Horizon Europe Regulation. Its general objectives are: to contribute towards the creation of a Union-wide health research and innovation ecosystem that facilitates translation of scientific knowledge into innovations; to foster the development of safe, effective, people-centred and cost-effective innovations that respond to strategic unmet public health needs; to drive cross-sectoral health innovation for a globally competitive European health industry, and contribute to reaching the objectives of the new Industrial Strategy for Europe and the Pharmaceutical Strategy for Europe."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "95207"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "FS"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "10.2879"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "IMI"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "IHIJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001650"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "IHIJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "IHIJU"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>;
