<#37dff5b48a2d8cd30f281047957d1782> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/FCH_2008_0>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:09.180Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#37dff5b48a2d8cd30f281047957d1782> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/FCH_2008_0> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "true";
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> true;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Entreprise commune «Piles à combustible et Hydrogène»"@fr, "Empresa comum «Pilhas de Combustível e Hidrogénio»"@pt, "Wspólne Przedsiębiorstwo na rzecz technologii ogniw paliwowych i technologii wodorowych"@pl, "Společný podnik pro palivové články a vodík"@cs, "Fuel Cells and Hydrogen Joint Undertaking"@en, "Kütuseelementide ja Vesiniku Valdkonna Ühisettevõte"@et, "Empresa Común «Pilas de Combustible e Hidrógeno»"@es, "Üzemanyagcella- és Hidrogéntechnológiai Közös Vállalkozás"@hu, "Skupno podjetje za gorivne celice in vodik"@sl, "Fællesforetagendet for brændselsceller og brint"@da, "Съвместното предприятие „Горивни клетки и водород“"@bg, "Κοινή Επιχείρηση «Κυψέλες Καυσίμου και Υδρογόνο»"@el, "Impresa comune «Celle a combustibile e idrogeno»"@it, "Întreprinderea comună „Pile de combustie și hidrogen”"@ro, "Gemeenschappelijke Onderneming brandstofcellen en waterstof"@nl, "Spoločný podnik pre palivové články a vodík"@sk, "Polttokenno- ja vety-yhteisyritys"@fi, "Zajedničko poduzeće za gorive ćelije i vodik"@hr, "Gemensamma företaget för bränsleceller och vätgas"@sv, "Gemeinsames Unternehmen „Brennstoffzellen und Wasserstoff“"@de, "Kuro elementų ir vandenilio bendroji įmonė"@lt, "Kopuzņēmums “Kurināmā elementi un ūdeņradis”"@lv, "An Gnóthas Comhpháirteach um Chealla Breosla agus um Hidrigin"@ga, "L-Impriża Konġunta taċ-Ċelloli tal-Fjuwil u L-Idroġenu"@mt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Fuel Cells and Hydrogen Joint Undertaking is a unique public private partnership supporting research, technological development and demonstration activities in fuel cell and hydrogen energy technologies in Europe. Its three members are the European Commission, fuel cell and hydrogen industries represented by the NEW Industry Grouping and the research community represented by Research Grouping N.ERGHY."@en;
