    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Empresa Comum do Setor Ferroviário Europeu"@pt, "L-Impriża Konġunta Sistema Ferrovjarja Ewropea"@mt, "Európai Vasút Közös Vállalkozás"@hu, "Fællesforetagendet for Europas jernbaner"@da, "Zajedničko poduzeće za europsku željeznicu"@hr, "Euroopa raudtee ühisettevõte"@et, "Skupno podjetje za evropske železnice"@sl, "Съвместно предприятие „Европейски железопътен транспорт“"@bg, "Europos geležinkelių bendroji įmonė"@lt, "Det gemensamma företaget för Europas järnvägar"@sv, "Wspólne Europejskie Przedsięwzięcie Kolejowe"@pl, "Κοινή επιχείρηση «Ευρωπαϊκοί σιδηρόδρομοι»"@el, "Europe’s Rail Joint Undertaking"@en, "Spoločný podnik pre európske železnice"@sk, "Gemeenschappelijke Onderneming “Europese spoorwegen”"@nl, "Gemeinsames Unternehmen für Europas Eisenbahnen"@de, "Comhghnóthas um Iarnród na hEorpa"@ga, "Euroopan rautatiet -yhteisyritys"@fi, "Întreprinderea comună pentru căile ferate ale Europei"@ro, "Kopuzņēmums “Eiropas dzelzceļš”"@lv, "Empresa Común para el Ferrocarril Europeo"@es, "Entreprise commune «Système ferroviaire européen»"@fr, "Společný podnik pro evropské železnice"@cs, "Impresa comune «Ferrovie europee»"@it;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Europe’s Rail Joint Undertaking is a public-private partnership which contributes to the general objectives of the Horizon Europe Regulation. Its general objectives are: to contribute towards the achievement of the Single European Railway Area; to ensure a fast transition to more attractive, user-friendly, competitive, affordable, efficient and sustainable European rail system, integrated into the wider mobility system; to support the development of a strong and globally competitive European rail industry."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "10.2881"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "95215"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "HI"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "EURAIL"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "EU-Rail"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "EURAIL"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "EURAIL"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>, "COB0001648"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
