    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Orgán európskych regulátorov pre elektronické komunikácie"@sk, "Organismo de Reguladores Europeos de las Comunicaciones Electrónicas"@es, "Sammenslutningen af Europæiske Tilsynsmyndigheder inden for Elektronisk Kommunikation"@da, "Tijelo europskih regulatora za elektroničke komunikacije"@hr, "Il-Korp ta’ Regolaturi Ewropej tal-Komunikazzjonijiet Elettroniċi"@mt, "Organismo dei regolatori europei delle comunicazioni elettroniche"@it, "Sdružení evropských regulačních orgánů v oblasti elektronických komunikací"@cs, "Орган на европейските регулатори в областта на електронните съобщения"@bg, "Organ Europejskich Regulatorów Łączności Elektronicznej"@pl, "Organe des régulateurs européens des communications électroniques"@fr, "Organet för europeiska regleringsmyndigheter för elektronisk kommunikation"@sv, "Body of European Regulators for Electronic Communications"@en, "Europos elektroninių ryšių reguliuotojų institucija"@lt, "Euroopan sähköisen viestinnän sääntelyviranomaisten yhteistyöelin"@fi, "Φορέας Ευρωπαϊκών Ρυθμιστικών Αρχών για τις Ηλεκτρονικές Επικοινωνίες"@el, "Organ evropskih regulatorjev za elektronske komunikacije"@sl, "Európai Elektronikus Hírközlési Szabályozók Testülete"@hu, "Orgaan van Europese regulerende instanties voor elektronische communicatie"@nl, "Gremium europäischer Regulierungsstellen für elektronische Kommunikation"@de, "Organismul Autorităților Europene de Reglementare în Domeniul Comunicațiilor Electronice"@ro, "Comhlacht na Rialálaithe Eorpacha um Chumarsáid Leictreonach"@ga, "Organismo dos Reguladores Europeus das Comunicações Eletrónicas"@pt, "Elektroonilise Side Euroopa Reguleerivate Asutuste Amet"@et, "Eiropas Elektronisko sakaru regulatoru iestāde"@lv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Body of European Regulators for Electronic Communications (BEREC) ensures independent, consistent, high-quality application of the European regulatory framework for electronic communications markets for the benefit of Europe and its citizens. BEREC contributes to the development and better functioning of the internal market for electronic communications networks and services. It does so, by aiming to ensure a consistent application of the EU regulatory framework and by aiming to promote an effective internal market in telecoms sector, in order to bring even greater benefits to consumers and businesses alike. Furthermore, BEREC assists the Commission and the national regulatory authorities (NRAs) in implementing the EU regulatory framework for electronic communications. It provides advice on request and on its own initiative to the European institutions and complements at European level the regulatory tasks performed at national level by the NRAs."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "EM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "BEREC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OJ>, "95204"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "BEREC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "10.2858"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "BEREC_1"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>, "BEREC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "BRC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "BEREC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001564"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
